Package model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Base64Image
    Base64Image extends Image et gere la creation d'une Image javafx par une string sous format base64
    Base64ImageFactory
    Factory qui cree des objects Base64Image sois a partir du string Base64 complete: data:image/jpeg;base64,...
    Client
    Client manage all that have to do with the Client side aspect of the connection between sockets it extends SocketManage that does most of the heavy lifting
    ClientThread
    Thread qui permet le Client de pas locker l'interface
    Context
    Context est une classe qui sert pour contenir toute les informations specifique pour le fonctionnement de l' application.
    FileMessage
    FileMessage is a class extending Message that is used to send file information and content via socket
    Message
    Message is a Serialized class that is used to send txt content, an ip address, and port to a socket
    Server
    Server manage all that have to do with the server side aspect of the connection between sockets it extends SocketManage that does most of the heavy lifting
    ServerThread
    Server thread make a thread to run the server without blocking the app main thread
    SocketManager
    this abstract class deal with the shared functionnality of the Server and the Client
    User
    this class is serialize to send User information (his name, image in base64 and his ip) via a socket.
